  "instructions": [
    "1. Heat oil in a large pot over medium heat.",
    "2. Sauté onion and garlic until softened.",
    "3. Add seitan and cook until lightly browned.",
    "4. Add tomatoes, water, fish sauce, and paprika.",
    "5. Bring stew to a boil, then reduce heat and simmer for 20 minutes.",
    "6. Season with salt and pepper to taste.",
    "7. Add bay leaves and continue to simmer for another 10 minutes.",
